  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00515', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關社會政策的論述有不同的理論觀點，認為「決策制定是處於各種利益相互競逐下，最直接的方式是 透過選民影響議會或者官僚的決策過程」，請問是那一個理論觀點？', '["菁英論", "多元論", "國家中心論", "統合論"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e8d72e9f85c4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "83986d7ed3c7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00516', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關社會政策執行的論述，下列何者錯誤？', '["公部門透過政策規劃，通過法令規章，以作為後續福利執行或者服務提供的依據", "在社會政策執行時，十分重視公私協力，以落實服務", "透過志願服務所提供福利服務，可依志工的自己意願執行，不需要受到相關法令的規範", "非正式部門，也是提供福利服務的方法之一"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e8d72e9f85c4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "83986d7ed3c7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00517', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關「社區主義模式」（communitarianmodel）的敘述，何者為正確？', '["社區居民在資本市場依其需求購買托育服務", "由公部門統籌，提供公共托育的服務", "透過安養機構提供長者的照顧服務", "非營利組織依在地需求，針對在地不利處境家庭內的兒少提供照顧服務"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e8d72e9f85c4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "83986d7ed3c7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00518', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列措施何項不屬於脫貧的服務？', '["著重工作福利與人力資本的服務", "結合金融機構推展微型貸款", "運用發展帳戶促成低所得家庭資產累積的能力", "強化全民健保，保障國民健康"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e8d72e9f85c4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "83986d7ed3c7", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
